statements.sql:
SELECT t.alias,
tt.title
FROM
(SELECT tag_id,
COUNT(tag_post.tag_id) AS tag_count
FROM tag_post
GROUP BY tag_id
ORDER BY tag_count DESC ) AS tp
LEFT JOIN tags AS t ON tp.tag_id = t.id
LEFT JOIN tag_translations AS tt ON tt.tag_id = t.id
WHERE tt.locale = 'en'
ORDER BY tag_count DESC;
